h3cStorageRef.name: h3cStorageRef
h3cStorageRef.contactinfo: Platform Team H3C Technologies Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China Http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
h3cStorageRef.description: This MIB define the textual convention of storage.

H3cStorageCapableState.name: H3cStorageCapableState
H3cStorageCapableState.description: An enumerated value which provides an indication of the capability state of a particular object. The value 'support' means the resource is enable to be managed, and the value 'notsupport' means not

H3cStorageEnableState.name: H3cStorageEnableState
H3cStorageEnableState.description: An enumerated value which provides an indication of the ability state of a particular object.

H3cStorageActionType.name: H3cStorageActionType
H3cStorageActionType.description: A control variable used to trigger an operator events, when read, always returns a value of invalid.

H3cStorageLedStateType.name: H3cStorageLedStateType
H3cStorageLedStateType.description: This object identifies the state of storage device's led. The value 'off' means the led is go out. The value 'on' means the led is on. The value 'blink' means the led is blinking.

H3cStorageOnlineState.name: H3cStorageOnlineState
H3cStorageOnlineState.description: An enumerated value means an resource is online or offline.

H3cLvIDType.name: H3cLvIDType
H3cLvIDType.description: A variable used to identifies the GUID(global universal identification) of the logic volume.

H3cSessionIDType.name: H3cSessionIDType
H3cSessionIDType.description: A hex string used to identifies the session between targets and initiators.

H3cWwpnListType.name: H3cWwpnListType
H3cWwpnListType.description: This object describes the format of WWPN(World Wide Port Name) numbers. An WWPN is a 16-byte Hex value. Separate the WWPN by comma if more than one WWPN is specified. e.g. 13af35d2f4ea6fbc,13af35d2f4ea6fad.

H3cStorageOwnerType.name: H3cStorageOwnerType
H3cStorageOwnerType.description: An enumerated value used in HA(High Availability) iSCSI target. The value 'spa' means the owner is the first storage processor, and 'spb' means another.

H3cExtendSelectPolicy.name: H3cExtendSelectPolicy
H3cExtendSelectPolicy.description: This object describes how to assign the storage space. The value 'differentAdapter' means select drives from different adapter/channel, system will look for space on another array only if it is on a separate adapter/channel. The value 'differentDrive' means select different drive, system will look for space on another array. The value 'anyDrive' means select any available drive, system will look for space on any array, including the original. The value 'none' means the way to assign the storage space is not specified, in this case the system will allocate the storage with the default criteria in the following order: 1. the storage from different adapter 2. the storage from different drive 3. the storage from any drive

H3cRaidIDType.name: H3cRaidIDType
H3cRaidIDType.description: A string used to identifies the raid's UUID(unique universal identification). e.g. c0a800a8-0000-07f5-0057-386e145eda44.

H3cSoftwareInfoString.name: H3cSoftwareInfoString
H3cSoftwareInfoString.description: A string used to identifies the information which software provided. e.g. [TARGET,LVM,DM] or [Both] or [3].
